  <main>
    <div class="container" id="main-content">

      <nav class="uikit-breadcrumbs" aria-label="breadcrumb">
        <ul class="uikit-link-list uikit-link-list--inline">
          <li>
            <a href="/styleguide">Home</a>
          </li>
          <li>Navigation</li>
        </ul>
      </nav>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-9">
          <h1>Navigation</h1>
          <div class="breakout">
            <p>Navigation elements are used within the MyService header, footer and process flows. Animated sliding panels are used for log in, for help during a process flow, and
            to access information on 24hr counselling and support services. Other global navigation elements include a 'Return to top' button.</p>
          </div>

          <h2>Header</h2>

          <p>There are three styling options used in the MyService header:</p>
          <ol>
            <li>
              <b>
                <a href="#default-header">Default header</a>
              </b>. The default header style.</li>
              <li>
                <b>
                  <a href="#reduced-header">Reduced header</a>
                </b>. A lighter and compact version of the default header.</li>
                <li>
                  <b>
                    <a href="#light-header">Light header</a>
                  </b>. Used only for the unauthenticated homepage.</li>

                </ol>

                <a name="default-header"></a>
                <h3>Default header</h3>
                <p>This style is used for all pages across MyService
                  <i>except</i> those that sit within a process flow (eg. making a claim for initial liability).</p>
                  <div class="example-box">

                    <a name="reduced-header"></a>
                    <h3>Reduced header</h3>
                    <p>This header style is used for pages that sit within a process flow (eg. making a claim for initial liability).</p>

                    <header class="uikit-header reduced-header">
                      <div class="container">
                        <img class="logo-myservice" src="/docs/images/logo-myservice.svg" alt="MyService logo" />
                      </div>
                    </header>

                    <pre>
                      <code class="language-markup">
                       <script type="text/plain">
                        <header class="uikit-header reduced-header">
                         <div class="container">
                          <img class="logo-myservice" src="/docs/images/logo-myservice.svg" alt="MyService logo" />
                        </div>
                      </header>
                    </script>
                  </code>
                </pre>

              </div>

              <a name="light-header"></a>
              <h3>Light header</h3>
              <p>This header style is used for the unathenticated homepage. That is, the page a user will see before they login to MyService.</p>
              <div class="example-box">
                <header class="uikit-header landing-page" style="position: relative">
                  <div class="container">
                    <img src="/docs/images/logo-dva-black.svg" alt="Department of Veteran's Affairs logo" />
                    <img class="logo-myservice" src="/docs/images/logo-myservice-reversed.svg" alt="MyService logo" />
                    <p class="header-login">
                      <a href="#" class="panel-btn">Log in</a>/</p>
                    </div>
                  </header>

                  <pre>
                    <code class="language-markup">
                     <script type="text/plain">
                      <header class="uikit-header landing-page">
                       <div class="container">
                        <img src="/docs/images/logo-dva-black.svg" alt="Department of Veteran's Affairs logo" />
                        <img class="logo-myservice" src="/docs/images/logo-myservice-reversed.svg" alt="MyService logo" />
                        <p class="header-login">
                         <a href="#" class="panel-btn">Log in</a>/</p>
                       </div>
                     </header>
                   </script>
                 </code>
               </pre>

             </div>

             <hr>

             <h2>Footer</h2>
             <p>The MyService footer is a global element and appears consistently across
              <b>all</b> pages. The DVA logo is featured prominently in the bottom left, inline with the
              <a href="https://www.dta.gov.au/standard/design-guides/branding/#mobile-websites" rel="external">Australian Government guides</a>, the logo size and positioning does
              not
            effecting the integrity of the logo.</p>

            <div class="example-box">
              <table>
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <footer class="uikit-footer uikit-footer--gradient" role="contentinfo">
                      <div class="container">
                        <div class="row">
                          <section class="uikit-footer__end">
                            <div class="row">
                              <div class="col-sm-4">
                                <img src="/docs/images/logo-dva-black.svg" alt="Department of Veteran's Affairs logo">
                              </div>
                              <div class="col-sm-9">
                                <ul class="uikit-link-list uikit-link-list--inline">
                                  <li>
                                    <a href="http://www.dva.gov.au/site-information/disclaimer">Disclaimer</a>
                                  </li>
                                  <li>
                                    <a href="http://www.dva.gov.au/site-information/privacy">Privacy and security</a>
                                  </li>
                                  <li>
                                    <a href="http://www.dva.gov.au/site-information/copyright">Copyright</a>
                                  </li>
                                  <li>
                                    <a href="/unauth/terms-and-conditions">Terms of use</a>
                                  </li>
                                  <li>
                                    <a href="http://www.dva.gov.au/" rel="external">
                                      <strong>Department of Veterans' Affairs</strong>
                                    </a>
                                  </li>
                                </ul>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </section>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </footer>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </div>

            <hr>

